  "summary": {
    "as": "Introduced", 
    "date": "1987-03-30", 
    "text": "Directs the Secretary of Defense, during FY 1988, to take all necessary action to enable certain systems and components of the Strategic Defense Initiative program to achieve certain specified deployment objectives. Directs the Secretary, no later than February 1 of each year, to make progress reports to the Congress on the deployment of such systems, as well as information on Soviet countermeasures to such system."
